{"tid":2118541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門富臨累計10人確診　食環署提檢控：食肆員工無戴口罩處理食物　餐桌間少於1.5米","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T14:02:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3cdcb4722c6cb9b114a301422bc20f5bdd49f58","tid":2118541,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"屯門中央廣場富臨酒家今日（21日）新增4人確診新型冠狀病毒，該處累計10人確診。食環署表示，昨日（20日）上午到該店巡查，發現有員工處理食物時未有戴口罩，餐桌之間也少於1.5米距離，已經向負責人提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨日向富臨查詢，7月11日的生日宴會上，一共有多少圍酒席、當晚酒家坐滿了多少成顧客、有否遵守第599F章規定；富臨回覆本報稱，「為配合政府抗疫措施，集團旗下餐館遵守規例招待顧客，為顧客提供安全及舒適的用餐環境」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200721/s00001/1595335522001/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e5%af%8c%e8%87%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%8810%e4%ba%ba%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba-%e9%a3%9f%e7%92%b0%e7%bd%b2%e6%8f%90%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7-%e9%a3%9f%e8%82%86%e5%93%a1%e5%b7%a5%e7%84%a1%e6%88%b4%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e8%99%95%e7%90%86%e9%a3%9f%e7%89%a9-%e9%a4%90%e6%a1%8c%e9%96%93%e5%b0%91%e6%96%bc1-5%e7%b1%b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200721%2Fs00001%2F1595335522001%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%25af%258c%25e8%2587%25a8%25e7%25b4%25af%25e8%25a8%258810%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba-%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2592%25b0%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e6%258f%2590%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7-%25e9%25a3%259f%25e8%2582%2586%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%2588%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e8%2599%2595%25e7%2590%2586%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2589%25a9-%25e9%25a4%2590%25e6%25a1%258c%25e9%2596%2593%25e5%25b0%2591%25e6%2596%25bc1-5%25e7%25b1%25b3&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=0cb754a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200721